As manthros's body lays lifeless on the ground, Denzu stands over him with 
whip in hand. "So, this is where the pod went, I take it you came out of it" 
He hits Manthors with the whip again, an electric shock makes the body jolt. 
He looks at Blackheart. "Do I know you......."
